      objectReference: {fileID: 7628849239691000561, guid: 1a9cfb2a0102c27459fdad9a911df0c9, type: 3}
    - target: {fileID: 934122727019215057, guid: 17dab5cc3d30d3347b03feeb9bb2fb03, type: 3}
      propertyPath: altLeftImages.Array.data[1].sprite
      value: 
      objectReference: {fileID: 7628849239691000561, guid: 1a9cfb2a0102c27459fdad9a911df0c9, type: 3}
    - target: {fileID: 934122727019215057, guid: 17dab5cc3d30d3347b03feeb9bb2fb03, type: 3}
      propertyPath: altLeftImages.Array.data[2].sprite
      value: 
      objectReference: {fileID: -6097340706306594537, guid: ac9726a943261874989ce49dacacd1bd, type: 3}
    - target: {fileID: 934122727019215057, guid: 17dab5cc3d30d3347b03feeb9bb2fb03, type: 3}
      propertyPath: altLeftImages.Array.data[3].sprite
      value: 
      objectReference: {fileID: -6097340706306594537, guid: ac9726a943261874989ce49dacacd1bd, type: 3}
    - target: {fileID: 934122727019215057, guid: 17dab5cc3d30d3347b03feeb9bb2fb03, type: 3}
      propertyPath: altLeftImages.Array.data[4].sprite
      value: 
      objectReference: {fileID: -6097340706306594537, guid: ac9726a943261874989ce49dacacd1bd, type: 3}
    - target: {fileID: 934122727019215057, guid: 17dab5cc3d30d3347b03feeb9bb2fb03, type: 3}
      propertyPath: altLeftImages.Array.data[5].sprite
      value: 
      objectReference: {fileID: -2164515400223056680, guid: ca03bef36c6864d4e93b8828baa0c10f, type: 3}
    - target: {fileID: 934122727019215057, guid: 17dab5cc3d30d3347b03feeb9bb2fb03, type: 3}
      propertyPath: altLeftImages.Array.data[6].sprite
      value: 
      objectReference: {fileID: -2164515400223056680, guid: ca03bef36c6864d4e93b8828baa0c10f, type: 3}
    - target: {fileID: 934122727019215057, guid: 17dab5cc3d30d3347b03feeb9bb2fb03, type: 3}
      propertyPath: altLeftImages.Array.data[7].sprite
      value: 
      objectReference: {fileID: -2164515400223056680, guid: ca03bef36c6864d4e93b8828baa0c10f, type: 3}
    - target: {fileID: 934122727019215057, guid: 17dab5cc3d30d3347b03feeb9bb2fb03, type: 3}
      propertyPath: altDialogueLines.Array.data[0].text
      value: Eeeeeh... this is odd... I'm pretty sure this wasn't on the map. Is
        this a shortcut or something?
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 934122727019215057, guid: 17dab5cc3d30d3347b03feeb9bb2fb03, type: 3}
      propertyPath: altDialogueLines.Array.data[1].text
      value: Oh, what a surprise, a human crossing my bridge... And attacking everyone
        while at it. Do you think this is funny?
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 934122727019215057, guid: 17dab5cc3d30d3347b03feeb9bb2fb03, type: 3}
      propertyPath: altDialogueLines.Array.data[2].text
      value: Hey, they attacked me first.
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 934122727019215057, guid: 17dab5cc3d30d3347b03feeb9bb2fb03, type: 3}
      propertyPath: altDialogueLines.Array.data[3].text
      value: You keep telling yourself that. I can understand that... but... it's
        more than 40 spirits, and half of them didn't mean to kill you... I'd think
        your boss would've let you know that.
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 934122727019215057, guid: 17dab5cc3d30d3347b03feeb9bb2fb03, type: 3}
      propertyPath: altDialogueLines.Array.data[4].text
      value: Or maybe you're doing this to please her. What I'd give to have such
        a good lackey.
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 934122727019215057, guid: 17dab5cc3d30d3347b03feeb9bb2fb03, type: 3}
      propertyPath: altDialogueLines.Array.data[5].text
      value: Who are you calling a lackey? And how did you figure out the fox part?
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 934122727019215057, guid: 17dab5cc3d30d3347b03feeb9bb2fb03, type: 3}
      propertyPath: altDialogueLines.Array.data[6].text
      value: 'Human, I can smell her stench from a mile away. '
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 934122727019215057, guid: 17dab5cc3d30d3347b03feeb9bb2fb03, type: 3}
      propertyPath: altDialogueLines.Array.data[7].text
      value: Ugh... remind me not to come through here again next time.
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 934122727019215057, guid: 17dab5cc3d30d3347b03feeb9bb2fb03, type: 3}
      propertyPath: altRightImages.Array.data[0].sprite
      value: 
      objectReference: {fileID: -3226775618893619534, guid: 57fc181c578d63648b4eb61f3099752f, type: 3}
